{"id":1226,"date":"2015-04-08T02:38:39","date_gmt":"2015-04-08T02:38:39","slug":"cons-project-los-angeles-design-and-build-your-own-deck","title":"CONS Project Los Angeles &#8211; Design &#038; and build your own deck","content":"<p>On 4th April 2015, <a href=\"http://www.converse.com/landing-cons\" target=\"_blank\">Converse CONS</a> held a design and build a deck event as part of the CONS Project Los Angeles with the support of <a href=\"http://www.createaskate.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Create A Skate</a> and <a href=\"http://www.activerideshop.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Active</a>. Create A Skate&#8217;s Chuck Hults, the brothers Cody and Jared Hager were on hand  to guide participants on how to design and shape their own decks, along with <a href=\"http://www.worldwideslave.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Slave&#8217;s</a> Ben Horton and <a href=\"http://www.lurkville.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lurkville</a>&#8216;s Dolan Stearns giving insights into the the process of  designing and making deck graphics. It was an all around amazing day for everyone!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1234 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_4633.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_4633\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_4633.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/IMG_4633.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/IMG_4633.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The morning started off with an introduction into deck technologies and a brief overview into the correct design steps to make sure everyone got their deck dimensions exactly the way they wanted.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The introduction with Jared, Chuck and Codi.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1229 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_4625.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_4625\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_4625.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/IMG_4625.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/IMG_4625.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With the help of Create A Skate template builders, this latter part of the process was made really easy, and the only real challenge was in deciding what kind of shape we each wanted, we were definitely spoiled for choice.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Active&#8217;s Eric is hyped for sure (Check his <a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/1Izzi-RqgH/?taken-by=smellington666\" target=\"_blank\">instagram</a> for the sick Coffin Cruiser shape he designed. Heck yeah Eric!!).</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1239 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_0279.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0279\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_0279.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0279.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The design template.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1240 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0286-e1428457853741.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0286\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0286-e1428457853741.jpg 225w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0286-e1428457853741.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a>With a short break for lunch, we were back busily getting our decks cut and belt sanded. Chuck Hults and the Hager brothers really took care of us with this, patiently guiding us and showing us the proper technique. Definitely learned a lot, and hopefully we weren&#8217;t too terrible with the jigsaw.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Codi explaining how to cut our decks.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1244 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_0283.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0283\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_0283.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0283.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Chuck demonstrating the proper technique to get those complicated curves cut nicely. Thanks Chuck!</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1242 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0306-e1428458677664.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0306\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0306-e1428458677664.jpg 225w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0306-e1428458677664.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Jared helping round out the edges. Thanks Jared!</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1243 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0308-e1428458692254.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0308\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0308-e1428458692254.jpg 225w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0308-e1428458692254.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The afternoon session consisted of a talk by <a href=\"http://www.worldwideslave.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Slave&#8217;s</a> Ben Horton on the process of designing deck graphics as well as him sharing some personal anecdotes on some of his favorite graphics. It was really cool to hear what inspires him, and to gain some insight into the whole artistic process. <a href=\"http://www.lurkville.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lurkville&#8217;s</a> <a href=\"https://instagram.com/sorry_entertainer/\" target=\"_blank\">Dolan Stearns</a> was also on hand to share his artistic influences and also to craft a deck of his own design. Not only is Dolan a ripper(he nollied and then impossibled over a trash can at the event) but he&#8217;s a super talented artist in his own right. To see him go through the whole process in person was totally rad!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Dolan sharing the stoke with Josh.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1245 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_0291.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0291\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_0291.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0291.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1252 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_46351.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_4635\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/IMG_46351.jpg 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/IMG_46351.jpg 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/IMG_46351.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Dolan with his finished deck. So friggin&#8217; rad!!</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1246 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0311-e1428459508811.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0311\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0311-e1428459508811.jpg 225w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0311-e1428459508811.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Got to see so many amazing shapes and graphics that day. We loved what we saw for sure!! Thank you Converse CONS for organizing this, and to Create A Skate and Active for making this such a memorable day for everyone. Dreams do come true!!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Salvador&#8217;s sick board, check out his art <a href=\"https://instagram.com/psilocybin__\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8&amp;ign-mpt=uo%3D4\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1248 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0312-e1428460069293.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0312\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_225/mag/uploads/IMG_0312-e1428460069293.jpg 225w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_0312-e1428460069293.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":"kev","categories":["event"],"tags":["active","ben-horton","chuck-hults","codi-hager","consproject","create-a-skate","dolan-stearns","jared-hager","los-angeles","lurkville"],"featuredImages":[{"file":"IMG_46351.jpg","width":2816,"height":2112,"mime_type":"image/jpeg","source_url":"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/IMG_46351.jpg"}],"video":""}